, 之前間廠由三來一補轉獨資時, 間廠既法人代表本來應由廠長做, 有事就捉廠長, 但佢信唔過人, 結果由佢自己做返法人, 而家脫唔到身, 間廠又做埋D假數, 一旦收皮, 實捉燃老細"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:30:49.000Z","msg":"捉你逃稅再封廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:33:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4c56958232826c3c54b0f6d41471bcf70f579c","tid":813102,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T10:12:42.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"f555521bf7a2d4f57965a45437a9b9aaf65115bf","tid":813102,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T11:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67ace1a5a696fda6f87a2ec3fd665a0a8d99c58","tid":813102,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5bc501c4d5517471eaf1b588d628871e47989c","tid":813102,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e642498ab0fa83d30938b670da31d36e3bdfbbcc","tid":813102,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}